During the audit, both normal business transactions were detected and those for which there was a suspicion of carousel fraud or other VAT fraud.
In these cases, the FA information exchanged in accordance with Council Regulation (EC) 1798/2003,
for example,:
* FÄ did not detect any suspicion of risky sales when examining early warning information.
The taxpayers concerned were continuously monitored because their data were stored in EUROCANET.
